data.description: Welcome to Simpson Crossing, with NO CITY TAXES, this spacious single-story home includes three bedrooms, with a bonus/flex room above the garage and two bathrooms. The home is well maintained, making it the ideal place to call home. As you approach the property, you are greeted by a covered front porch. Step inside to discover a spacious and inviting living area with high ceilings, complete with laminate floors throughout the main floor. The cozy fireplace is perfect for those chilly winter nights. The kitchen is open to the living area with stainless steel appliances, plenty of cabinet space, and a pantry for storage. The adjacent dining area is perfect for entertaining guests or enjoying meals. The home offers three bedrooms, each with ample closet space and laminate floors. The owner's suite includes a walk-in closet, dual vanities and a linen closet in the bathroom. Head into the backyard there is a spacious deck and fenced in backyard perfect for hosting summer BBQs or simply enjoying the beautiful North Carolina weather. The property also features a separate laundry room, a two-car garage and a large driveway, providing plenty of parking space for guests. Located a short distance from military bases, shopping, dining, beaches, and entertainment options. With its unbeatable location and charming features, NO CITY TAXES, don't miss out on the opportunity to make this your home, schedule your private showing today!
